{"tid":116841,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"王者，傳說，獵神 邊隻最好","createTime":"2017-02-11T17:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T09:01:41.000Z","uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00ec68ab7af8f800ed64e7f330fa4cc6941bc025","tid":116841,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"王者同傳說都有玩<br />\n日日開咪屌鳩蝗同台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f008ba418318e5ad7acbc5b2836b7a0861b79c","tid":116841,"uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"只玩過獵神,目前得29隻英,17日出一隻新英.<br />\n最貴英雄12888,最平2888,一場有70$,平均13分鐘一場"},{"pid":"0f19e2a78df5397d51e119638f8c2a85a1295202","tid":116841,"uid":75754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"獵神比我感覺有啲lag 控制方面唔流暢<br />\n傳說比較順 都玩得比較多<br />\n王者 好似大陸appstore先有 有其他選擇下都唔揀佢"},{"pid":"73eff30d519577198b8e59178a0a7cf1b77d4a53","tid":116841,"uid":33595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"玩緊傳說感覺幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b57d7c7294c990065c216ff65121efaacdcd87a","tid":116841,"uid":6614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"傳說for sure"},{"pid":"503ce72aee2cdf08f3020ffd4a2084c440e0aa72","tid":116841,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:11:08.000Z","msg":"王者， 一見殘體已經唔想玩， 同獵神一樣d畫風卡通得濟， 玩開傳說"},{"pid":"4b571f62e01eb7c3502cf1cd146066dfbcf057fc","tid":116841,"uid":25522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"王者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee59b85645671281ce6eca3396f2ec836837feef","tid":116841,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"王者真係流暢d"},{"pid":"5c995c2f962f5ee861d582f40419b12db955138b","tid":116841,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"王者<br />\n獵神係qq既棄game,之前叫全民超神，做白老鼠既<br />\n之後用佢等番來既數據來做基礎研發王者<br />\n跟住就比垃圾efun代理左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大陸個邊已收皮<br />\n<br />\n王者係qq旗下天美出品，qq自營<br />\n傳說都係天美出品，按王者既陷來做，之後比qq旗下既gerena係台灣做代理，但半棄，你地對比番就知<br />\n同一隻英，比如王者既典偉=傳說既趙雲，天美係王者個邊一早已知唔平衡重做左一二技，但係傳說就一路無改動，因為根本唔想理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fe98fd235e0968771e51f4fa23e9fc19ea4a79","tid":116841,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T01:04:04.000Z","msg":"但係獵神d配音幾過癮"},{"pid":"f42d7eff07b12be76ab22ef7f5547ffeeae8c816","tid":116841,"uid":14565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"3隻我都有玩<br />\n一開始我係玩獵神先 但玩左一日已經唔想玩<br />\nD畫質一般 同埋唔知點解入草叢都會俾D卒見到<br />\n<br />\n之後轉左玩傳說<br />\n傳說感覺流暢度高好多 畫面又靚好多<br />\n後尾玩左一段時間 先知道佢係台版既王者榮耀<br />\n<br />\n之後我就下載左王者黎玩<br />\n王者D畫面比起傳說 我更鐘意前者 D SKIN真係好鬼靚<br />\n但有D地方要彈<br />\nD英雄通常一出果時係好鬼勁 但後尾係咁俾人削 甚至重制<br />\n同埋佢可以用WECHAT / QQ登入 但係個SER就唔同<br />\n仲有仲有 假設你係用IPHONE 用QQ登入黎玩<br />\n如果你有一日轉用AN機 EVEN你用番同一個QQ帳號登入 D數據都會冇左<br />\n依樣野真係好麻煩 因為我用IPHONE玩左一段時間 有課金 但我準備換AN機 變左要重玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但整體上 王者真係正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸GAME 課金靠淘寶代充 我充過好多次都冇事 記得改密碼就得"},{"pid":"ecea296ec570d9a73601a9e179ac7ffaef2617cb","tid":116841,"uid":49180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"王者 畫質 流暢度都好過其他2隻<br />\n利申；三隻都玩過"},{"pid":"0e3348d56edac42d612acae2aa186921d2b88fd7","tid":116841,"uid":52961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:06:59.000Z","msg":"三隻都有玩 <br />\n但我會buy王者<br />\n多英多skin有其它玩法<br />\n傳說已經棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f166d05ef1931b4f0dc773700e346538db01ec3","tid":116841,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T00:49:05.000Z","msg":"3隻都玩哂"},{"pid":"22c70e14b3efb899bce7c2f544c9f582ac1ca79e","tid":116841,"uid":7808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"王者for sure<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  畫質 流暢 都比其他兩隻好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdaaebbe67fc761b8803185ada1f90df6056cc4","tid":116841,"uid":17222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"王者<br />\n利申鑽"},{"pid":"5054da5aeaa4fe0acf6a546f4348ca9a3e970eea","tid":116841,"uid":69698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"王者鑽 傳說s <br />\n傳說好玩d 但小英"}]}